data.description: Move in ready home in great location! Awesome one story located in Meadowbrook Estates subdivision! Open floor plan with laminate and ceramic tile through out, eat in kitchen with plenty of cabinet space and walk in pantry, spacious living area with built in shelving, and great sized bedrooms! Main suite features a walk in closet with full remodeled bath. Huge back yard with covered patio and privacy fence!
